E. R. Parker, Appellant, v. J. A. Timberlake, etc., Appellee. An Appeal from the Circuit Court for the County of Polk. Rogers & Rogers, for Appellant; Treadwell & Treadwell, Brown & Jones, and J. A. Timberlake, for Appellee.
